onster.axd%3fseed%3d79a775c423%26size%3d80"></P>
<P class=3Dcontent><CITE title=3DQuote>Im not sure why there would be =
more than one=20
version at this stage in time.</CITE> <BR>The ITTF might be doing some =
editorial=20
cleanup on the project editors work ? Making it more ISO styled ? =
<BR>SC34 has=20
the project editors version which then of course might slightly differ =
from the=20
official one. Could be anoying and confusing especially if the paging or =

numbering changes.</P>
